####	HOW TO USE THIS MODULE	####

Step 1 : Install Puppetlabs Mysql Module, Puppet labs APT and Puppet Stdlib modules. 

Step 2 : Configure Hiera as we are passing IP addresses using Hiera 

Step 3 : Copy and paste the site.pp,hiera.yaml and common.yaml  files found in example directory of this  module 
		 (assign values as per your requirement)


#### Example Files can be found in examples directory located in Percona Module ###
